name: doct
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.5" %}

package:
  name: doct
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: http://github.com/NSLS-II/doct/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  fn: doct-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f83b30e32feaf332f4c009582c63f772e9660040cdb7d6e5c3f9318811a8a5e0

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - humanize
    - prettytable
    - python
    - six
    - setuptools
  run:
    - humanize
    - prettytable
    - python
    - six 

test:
  imports:
    - doct

about:
  home: https://github.com/NSLS-II/document
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  summary: A read-only dottable dictionary

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ericdill
    - CJ-Wright
    - tacaswell
    - licode
    - danielballan
